{"tid":1215362,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律小知識]良好市民被警察搜查時的應對","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T09:35:58.000Z","uid":65354,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7516d2ccec6f7bac504e3eafb8d200e8bdf76d4","tid":1215362,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJTurSi0LhJs&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=4d6dc77f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除左基本資料外乜柒都唔好講 因為你有權唔答 <br />\n<br />\n然後就係問佢係咪要拘留 如果唔係拘留即係走得 佢警例232章54條嘅權力已經用完<br />\n</span></span><em><span style=\"color: pink;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(d) 扣留該人一段為作出該項搜查而合理需要的期間。</span></ins></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n如果佢唔係拘捕又唔肯放人，記得幫佢溫一溫警例 然後同佢上級/警察投訴課投訴佢唔熟讀警例</span></span>"},{"pid":"d85bcb1d84b8261c408feeba591825d38fb46bd7","tid":1215362,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:58:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e22e077eeb9439d007caf5a08c26d7285b80e64e","tid":1215362,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a0c8409cd981677bf296d92cb4b96bc9c1d25c93","tid":1215362,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5ee5784217de9b479b59277bfe76ec9c6fe2905","tid":1215362,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:35:58.000Z","msg":"同佢上級/警察投訴課投訴 完"}]}